but the outcome wasn't too good.

00:13:26.750 --> 00:13:28.590
But we'll get them later, I'm sure.

00:13:28.590 --> 00:13:30.460
So that's pretty cool.

00:13:30.460 --> 00:13:33.070
So now let's go into some of
the business side of this.

00:13:33.070 --> 00:13:34.420
Let's talk about some costs.

00:13:34.420 --> 00:13:36.210
Well, so you have setup costs.

00:13:36.220 --> 00:13:38.350
You've got to get
yourself some computers,

00:13:38.350 --> 00:13:41.020
and I actually have a
typical kind of setup here.

00:13:41.590 --> 00:13:42.940
Oh, this is really only kind of prop.

00:13:43.020 --> 00:13:45.460
This really isn't all connected up,
so we actually could broadcast,

00:13:45.470 --> 00:13:47.240
but we probably won't, but it looks nice.

00:13:47.370 --> 00:13:48.610
So I have a nice studio mic here.

