And you're supposed
to follow these rules.

00:27:45.180 --> 00:27:46.980
They give you a little leeway,
but you're supposed to

00:27:46.980 --> 00:27:48.060
roughly follow these rules.

00:27:49.540 --> 00:27:52.480
It's, you know,
a little bit of a restriction,

00:27:52.500 --> 00:27:55.170
but it's something that, you know,
traditional broadcasters

00:27:55.280 --> 00:27:56.040
